tissueExpression.summary: Adrenal gland along with a subset of germinal and non-germinal center cells in tonsil showed distinct cytoplasmic staining. A subset of cells in seminiferus ducts of testis displayed moderate dot-like nuclear staining. Moderate membranous staining was observed in a fraction of placental decidual cells. Remaining normal tissues were negative.
